      "writtenOn": "2019-10-23T10:16:32Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "If you wanted to avoid the possibility that buffer_ was reallocated, this would have to be \u003e\u003d kMaxBuffer, and it would also need to be done every time you push_back.",
